Package ie.gmit.dip

Class WordDetails

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.dip.WordDetails
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class WordDetails
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Since:
    1.8 The WordDetails class is a bean class that is used for storing a word definition.

    It stores word, word type and word definition. It may be used for storing a dictionary definition.

    It is Serializable.

    See Also:
